query TTT
EXPLAIN SELECT * FROM t JOIN u USING (a) FOR UPDATE
----
·                distribution        local
·                vectorized          true
render           ·                   ·
 └── merge-join  ·                   ·
      │          type                inner
      │          equality            (a) = (a)
      │          left cols are key   ·
      │          right cols are key  ·
      │          mergeJoinOrder      +"(a=a)"
      ├── scan   ·                   ·
      │          table               t@primary
      │          spans               FULL SCAN
      │          locking strength    for update
      └── scan   ·                   ·
·                table               u@primary
·                spans               FULL SCAN
·                locking strength    for update

